Yao to announce his retirement on Wednesday 
2011-07-19 08:47:36 GMT
SHANGHAI, July 19 (Xinhua) -- Yao Ming, the most popular basketball player in China, will officially announce his retirement at a press conference on Wednesday afternoon.Yao Ming's team of managers have booked a large reception hall at a hotel in Yao's hometown - the Pudong section of Shanghai. According to Yao's team, over 100 news organizations have applied to cover the press conference that will start at 2:00 pm.China's state television CCTV said they would run a four-hour program on Yao Ming Wednesday afternoon, including a live broadcast of the press conference. 

